# Intuition
<!-- Describe your first thoughts on how to solve this problem. -->

- Suppose, we have an arithmetic subarray (say X) of length k
- Then, number of subarrays in X having length 3 = k-2
            number of subarrays in X having length 4 = k-3
            ...
            number of subarrays in X having length k = k - (k-1)
            number of subarrays in X having length 0 = k - (k)  `// adding just to ease our calculation`

- Total number of subarrays in X:
![image.png](https://assets.leetcode.com/users/images/c0996972-7e78-40ef-9f3e-fa3d5bd2e861_1668822782.2685335.png)



# Complexity
- Time complexity: O(n)
<!-- Add your time complexity here, e.g. $$O(n)$$ -->

